[30;1m114 | [0m[35m  between them at runtime), but by defining `HUF_FORCE_DECOMPRESS_X1` or[0m
[30;1m115 | [0m[35m  `HUF_FORCE_DECOMPRESS_X2`, you can force the use of one or the other, avoiding[0m
[30;1m116 | [0m[35m  compilation of the other. Similarly, `ZSTD_FORCE_DECOMPRESS_SEQUENCES_SHORT`[0m

[30;1m485 | [0m[35mstatic int zlib_wrap_decompress(const void* input, int compressed_length,[0m
[30;1m486 | [0m[35m                                void* output, int maxout) {[0m
[30;1m487 | [0m[35m  int status;[0m
[30;1m488 | [0m[35m  uLongf ul = maxout;[0m
[30;1m489 | [0m[35m  status = uncompress([0m
